items.title: Manipal Hospitals & EQT emerge front-runners for buyout of Ontario Teachers backed Sahyadri Hospitals
items.description: As part of its first control private equity buyout in India in 2022, Canadian pension fund Ontario Teachers Pension Plan (OTPP) acquired a majority stake in Pune based Sahyadri Hospitals Group from the Everstone Group

items.title: Torrent Pharma to acquire controlling stake in JB Pharma from KKR at Rs 25,689 crore valuation
items.description: The transaction between Torrent and JB Pharma will unfold in two distinct phases.
